<%= render "mailers/shared/header",
    title: "Achievement Unlocked!",
    company_name: "My Custom Sleep Journey" %>

<div style="padding: 0 30px 20px; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6;">

  <p>Dear Dr. <strong><%= @user.last_name %></strong>,</p>

  <p>
    Hard work and consistency deserve recognition. We are thrilled to announce
    that you have officially earned the <strong><%= @badge_name %></strong> badge!
  </p>

  <p>
    This milestone is a testament to your dedication to your health, despite
    the challenges of your demanding medical schedule. Whether it’s hitting
    a streak of perfect nutrition or consistently syncing your Oura data, you
    are making measurable progress toward peak recovery.
  </p>

  <h3>Your Progress Snapshot:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>New Badge:</strong> <%= @badge_name %></li>
    <li><strong>Milestone Achieved:</strong> <%= @milestone %></li>
    <li><strong>Total Badges Earned:</strong> <%= @total_badges %></li>
  </ul>

  <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold;">
    Keep the Momentum Going:
  </p>

  <p>
    Log in to your dashboard to view your trophy case and see what’s next on your journey
    to better sleep and performance.
  </p>

  <%= render "mailers/shared/button",
      text: "View My Achievements",
      url: @dashboard_url %>

  <p style="margin-top: 25px;">
    Congratulations on this achievement!<br>
    <strong style="color:#0e3264;">
      The My Custom Sleep Journey Team
    </strong>
  </p>
</div>

<%= render "mailers/shared/footer",
    note: "This is an automated notification. No reply is required.",
    company_name: "My Custom Sleep Journey" %>
